data.description: WELCOME HOME! Beautiful custom home that won't disappoint! From the minute you walk in, you feel at home. With brand new LVP flooring throughout the entire main floor, basement, as well as the stairs, hall and main bedroom. Custom bookshelves and fireplace in the family room with a unique mantel that pulls out for storage! The kitchen has beautiful quartz countertops, tile backsplash, automatic faucet and new stove and dishwasher. Arched doorways will lead you to the dining room and foyer. Every room has been freshly painted and adds a coziness to this home you won't soon forget. Be sure not to miss the fabulous updated laundry room with upgraded lighting, wallpaper and retractable folding shelf. The primary bedroom is sure to delight with it's own electric fireplace, sitting area and romantic wall colors. All of the bedrooms are spacious and ready for new memories. The fully finished basement could easily be rented out or made in to a perfect in-law suite. With ample space for a kitchen and den, there is a full bath and finished area perfect for a bedroom. It has it's own private entrance around back with walk-up steps to a fully fenced in back-yard. The large screened-in porch with gorgeous wood ceiling and trex decking is sure to be the perfect space to entertain or enjoy your cup of coffee in the mornings. Another added feature are the solar panels that begin saving you money from day 1!  Don't miss your opportunity to make this beauty your own! Just minutes to Dahlgren Naval Base, shopping, Potomac River, or Harry Nice Bridge in to Maryland.
